data.title: IBC: John Martin Smith DeKalb County Heritage Fund Launch
data.text:
This project, coordinated by current DeKalb County Historian John Bry, celebrates the contributions of the late John Martin Smith, who served as DeKalb County Historian for more than a quarter of a century. This fund in his memory at the DeKalb County Community Foundation is a lasting legacy that will provide a celebratory endowment designed to foster and support the preservation, promotion and interpretation of De Kalb County’s history that is all-inclusive, supports programs for youth understanding of local heritage, and celebrates the history and heritage of the county as part of the state’s bicentennial year.

Organization: DeKalb County Historian & DeKalb County

County: DeKalb

Contact: John Bry, 239-321-4712, sowles88@yahoo.com
